<http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Ontology> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "This ontology includes medical devices, catalogued within the regulatory frameworks European MDR (EU 2017/745) and IVDR (EU 2017/746). Its purpose is to represent medical devices, their manufacturers, risks, incidents and corrective actions."@en .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Medical Devices Ontology"@en .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Miguel Ángel Barnés Torrente"@en .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Ontology for incidents, risk and actions related to medical devices."@en .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Medical Devices Ontology"@en .
