<http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/addressesIncident> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Relates a Field Safety Corrective Action (FSCA) to the specific incident it aims to mitigate or resolve."@en .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/addressesIncident> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "addresses incident"@en .
