<http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/affectsDeviceType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/Risk> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/affectsDeviceType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/Device> .
