<http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/country_reported> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/Incident> .
