<http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/hasCountry> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/Manufacturer> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/hasCountry> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://schema.org/Country> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/hasCountry> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a manufacturer or an incident report to the specific country or geographical region involved."@en .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/hasCountry> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has country"@en .
