<http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/hasManufacturer> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/Device> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/hasManufacturer> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/Manufacturer> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/hasManufacturer> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The relationship between a medical device and the legal entity responsible for its design and production."@en .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/hasManufacturer> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has manufacturer"@en .
