<http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/hasProbability> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/Risk> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/hasProbability> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/Probability> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/hasProbability> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a specific Risk to its estimated likelihood of occurrence (e.g., Low, Medium, High)."@en .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/hasProbability> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has probability"@en .
