<http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/hasRegulatoryFramework> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Associates a medical device with its applicable legal framework, such as MDR or IVDR."@en .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/hasRegulatoryFramework> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has regulatory framework"@en .
