<http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/hasRisk> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Associates a medical device with a potential hazard or risk identified during its lifecycle."@en .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/hasRisk> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has risk"@en .
