<http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/hasRiskCategory> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/RiskCategory> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/hasRiskCategory> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Classifies a Risk into a specific functional category, such as Device Failure or Patient Harm."@en .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/hasRiskCategory> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has risk category"@en .
# 
