<http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/hasRiskClass> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/Device> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/hasRiskClass> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/RiskClass> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/hasRiskClass> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Connects a device to its regulatory risk classification."@en .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/hasRiskClass> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has risk class"@en .
