<http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/hasSeverity> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Relates a Risk to the magnitude of its potential consequences or impact on health."@en .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/hasSeverity> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has severity"@en .
