<http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/hasStatus> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/FSCA> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/hasStatus> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/Status> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/hasStatus> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Indicates the current stage of a Field Safety Corrective Action, such as Open, Closed, or Pending."@en .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/hasStatus> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has status"@en .
