<http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/regulatedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Relates a medical device or manufacturer to the specific regulatory framework (MDR/IVDR) it must comply with."@en .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/regulatedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "regulated by"@en .
# 
# http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/reportedBy
<http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/reportedBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
