<http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/reportedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Relates an Incident to the manufacturer or entity responsible for submitting the official safety report."@en .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/migue/ontologies/MedicalDevicesOntology/reportedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "reported by"@en .
